AUDIO: 'Gmail, Docs, Slides, and more. The key difference is that Spark is cloud-based, so it can keep working after you close your laptop or lock your phone. Think of it like an AI assistant that can monitor a task, keep track of information, and'

[11:36] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'help complete workflows over time. You could teach it to check your inbox for school updates, pull out important deadlines, or send a daily summary to you and your partner. Or you can ask it to take raw meeting notes from emails'

