VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'actually need. It can help you shape your question with AI suggestions that go beyond just old-school autocomplete. And you can search with more than just text. You can use images, files, videos, or even Chrome tabs as inputs. So this'

[12:42] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'takes whatever context you have, whether that\'s a photo, and turns it into a question search can understand. The experience also becomes more conversational. This is where Google Search feels less like a search engine'

[12:55] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'and more like a set of AI helpers that can keep working after you ask. Google is starting with information agents which run in the background 24/7 and monitor the web for whatever you care about. Basically, you give the agent a'

